{"tid":453990,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"飛起來為甚麼會痛？","createTime":"2017-10-31T17:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T18:09:59.000Z","uid":114271,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5fe826a379c8ed07fedf71d205b42e75afcc4521","tid":453990,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T17:12:03.000Z","msg":"飛起來之所以痛<br />\n不僅僅因爲遠離了一切而痛<br />\n更是因爲儘管你變得比一切還輕<br />\n你還是不夠輕<br />\n你還是感到了自己微不足道的重量<br />\n<br />\n生命中不能承受的輕<br />\n就是如此<br />\n<br />\n因為 真正的無重<br />\n是與生命毫無關係<br />\n只要死亡 我們就都變得比一切還輕了"},{"pid":"917a8d11f896cdd05109dab0f61c3359be36a324","tid":453990,"uid":3581,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:32:21.000Z","msg":"有重先係飛<br />\n<br />\n無重, 並唔係飛"},{"pid":"300d65ebf460a9dbf68007819d5509773ee87c71","tid":453990,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有重先係飛<br />\n<br />\n無重, 並唔係飛</blockquote><br />\n我有冇講無重係飛<br />\n你自己答我"},{"pid":"beb6080f50ad6a9b15fd89eeb1c9b7af575bb9ff","tid":453990,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有重先係飛<br />\n<br />\n無重, 並唔係飛</blockquote><br />\n我有冇講無重係飛<br />\n你自己答我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有無講無重係飛都同無重唔係飛無關係"},{"pid":"e581b9b772662fe331126c423dd3c2812ae2ee9d","tid":453990,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有重先係飛<br />\n<br />\n無重, 並唔係飛</blockquote><br />\n我有冇講無重係飛<br />\n你自己答我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有無講無重係飛都同無重唔係飛無關係</blockquote><br />\n我講飛點解會痛 話係因為有重<br />\n咁無重仲係咪飛啊醒目仔<br />\n簡單邏輯都冇？"},{"pid":"bd2436e5098c41bf6c1c4e71d47d27239993cc57","tid":453990,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:07:15.000Z","msg":"睇topic以為問解坐飛機會耳仔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主係咪想講類似伊卡洛斯果啲？"},{"pid":"119263136be3194ceaacefa